description: Full planning permission for the demolition of existing building and redevelopment of the site comprising the erection of a building to include light industrial floorspace and Purpose-Built Student Accommodation, together with ancillary facilities, cycle parking, plant and associated works. Further explanation (not forming part of the formal description of development set out above):The proposed development includes the demolition of existing building and redevelopment of the site comprising the erection of a building up to 18 storeys high to include 1,032 sqm of light industrial floorspace (Use Class E(g)(iii)) and 348 Purpose-Built Student Accommodation rooms, together with ancillary facilities, cycle parking, plant and associated works.
